voxelforge is intended as a preliminary-design tool. Outputs are engineering
estimates subject to the uncertainty bands documented in
`Voxelforge/docs/PHYSICS.md` and `Voxelforge/docs/LIMITATIONS.md`.
Operating any hot-fire hardware derived from these outputs is at the operator's
